  # Predicting danceability and song ratings using deep learning and auditory features
  
  [Wei Wu](https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Wu%20W%22[Author])
  
  ### Wei Wu
  
  1Xiamen Medical College, Xiamen, Fujian, China
  
